      "Text": "Security update for wpa_supplicant",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for wpa_supplicant fixes the following issue:\n\n- CVE-2025-24912: hostapd RADIUS authentication of wi-fi devices allows a user in between the hostapd and the RADIUS\n  server to inject crafted RADIUS packets and force RADIUS authentications to fail (bsc#1239461).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
